The '''Equatorial Belt''' of [[Sevarcos II]] was the [[Spice/Legends|spice]]-rich equatorial area covered with endless plains. During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], it was ruled by the powerful [[Spice lord|Spice Lord]] [[Cassius Nolath Rha]].<ref name="The Free-Trader's Guide to Sevarcos">{{JournalCite|2|The Free-Trader's Guide to Sevarcos}}</ref>

